V0305_01_00_00_0.text:
I won't back down from a challenge!
Let's Duel!

V0305_01_00_02_0.text: If you're ready, I'm good to go!

V0305_01_00_05_0.text: Do you really think you can become a pro Duelist, Joey?

V0305_01_00_06_0.text: Whoever loses treats the winner to ice cream!

V0305_01_00_07_0.text:
Is that you, Mokuba?
You look so mature!

V0305_01_00_08_0.text:
Umm...
What was your name again?
...Oh! Aigami, right?

V0305_03_00_00_0.text: I like how this Duel is going!

V0305_05_00_00_0.text: This draw is for all or nothing!

V0305_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0305_08_00_00_0.text: I'll use the Ritual Spell, Commencement Dance!

V0305_08_00_01_0.text: I'll blow you away with my Spell Card, Breath of Light!

V0305_08_00_01_1.text: The wind erodes your Rock Monsters to dust!

V0305_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Dark Magic Inheritance!

V0305_08_00_03_0.text: I'll use this card to call Dark Magician!

V0305_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Bond Between Teacher and Student!

V0305_08_00_05_0.text: Dark Magician Girl, lend Dark Magician your strength!

V0305_08_00_06_0.text: Dark Magician Girl, blast 'em with your magic!

V0305_08_00_07_0.text: The master and student combine their talents!

V0305_08_00_07_1.text: The Quick-Play Spell, Dark Burning Magic!

V0305_08_00_08_0.text:
I'll use my Quick-Play Spell!
Dark Magic Expanded!

V0305_08_00_10_0.text: Due to Magic Formula's effect, I gain LP!

V0305_08_00_11_0.text: Even when things get tough, I know my friends are with me!

V0305_08_00_13_0.text: Watch the master and student work together!

V0305_08_00_13_1.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Magicians' Combination!

V0305_08_00_15_0.text: I'll use Magicians' Combination's additional effect!

V0305_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Magician's Circle!

V0305_08_00_18_0.text: I activate Magician Navigation's effect from my Graveyard!

V0305_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Magicians' Defense!

V0305_08_00_20_0.text: Magicians' Defense activates when it goes to the Graveyard!

V0305_08_00_21_0.text: I never say no to a dance off... but maybe I should.

V0305_09_00_00_0.text: I use Dancing Fairy's effect to increase my LP!

V0305_09_00_03_0.text: Berry Magician Girl adds a Magician Girl to my hand!

V0305_09_00_04_0.text: Berry Magician Girl brings out her friend!

V0305_09_00_05_0.text: I activate Lemon Magician Girl's effect!

V0305_09_00_06_0.text:
Too bad!
Lemon Magician Girl's effect activates!

V0305_09_00_07_0.text: Apple Magician Girl invites her friend to this Duel!

V0305_09_00_09_0.text: Chocolate Magician Girl's effect lets me draw a card!

V0305_09_00_10_0.text: When Chocolate Magician Girl is attacked, she calls an ally!

V0305_09_00_11_0.text: I discard Kiwi Magician Girl to activate her effect!

V0305_09_00_12_0.text: Apprentice Illusion Magician adds Dark Magician to my hand!

V0305_09_00_13_0.text: Now's the time to use Apprentice Illusion Magician's effect!

V0305_09_00_13_1.text: My monster gains 2000 ATK and DEF!

V0305_11_01_00_0.text: I'll Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0305_13_00_07_0.text:
Come on out!
Chocolate Magician Girl!

V0305_13_00_08_0.text: I believe in you, Kiwi Magician Girl!

V0305_13_00_09_0.text: I can sure use your help, Dark Magician Girl!

V0305_13_00_10_0.text: I can always count on you, Dark Magician Girl!

V0305_28_00_01_0.text:
That was so much fun!
Let's Duel again!

V0305_28_00_02_0.text: By winning this Duel, I feel more confident in my skills!

V0305_28_00_04_0.text:
I did it!!!
I beat Yugi!!!

V0305_28_00_05_0.text: Joey, you can't seriously be this weak.

V0305_28_00_06_0.text:
Will you take Dueling seriously?
Or you'll never be a pro!

V0305_29_00_00_0.text:
Sigh...
I thought I'd do better than this...

V0305_29_00_03_0.text:
You're still as strong as always.
Just as I hoped!

V0305_29_00_04_0.text:
Nice, Yugi!
This is why I know you'll achieve your dreams!

V0305_29_00_05_0.text: I was worried you weren't taking your future seriously.

V0305_29_00_05_1.text: But it seems I had nothing to worry about!

V0305_29_00_06_0.text: Who knows how often we'll get to play each other...

V0305_29_00_06_1.text:
So let's make every Duel count!
I won't lose next time!

V0305_33_00_00_0.text: If I'm Dueling, I'm Dueling to win!

V0305_34_00_03_0.text: You don't know what cards I have in my deck!

V0305_34_00_04_0.text: Always slather ketchup on your hamburger!

V0305_34_00_05_0.text: I'm not lucky! I have skills!

V0305_34_00_06_0.text:
Hmm...
You're so quiet...
That's spooky...

V0305_34_00_08_0.text: Sorry! Did I keep you waiting?

V0305_35_00_01_0.text: If I'm here, I'm ready to play!

V0305_36_00_02_0.text: I'm sorry... But I believe in you!

V0305_36_00_03_0.text: We're down to the final push!

V0305_36_00_05_0.text: Sorry! But I know you can fix this!

V0305_41_00_00_0.text: Is this a new type of Dueling?
